item.title: CVE-2013-2060|2024-08-06T15:20:37.415Z -- red%20hat -- openshift%20origin
item.description: The download_from_url function in OpenShift Origin allows remote attackers to execute arbitrary commands via shell metacharacters in the URL of a request to download a cart.
